text: Pogonocherus sturanii is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Sama and Schurmann in 1982. It is known from Spain.BioLib.cz - Pogonocherus sturanii. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Pogonocherini Category:Beetles described in 1982
